        "TileImage": "$($repository 81c949ff-c1d0-4c84-97ab-e1658d4da2b0).Image",
        "Description": "Welcome back, 47,\r\rWe have recieved a series of contracts to take down members of a covert organization called The Masquerade. The members of this organization hide amongst the public and seek to recruit members for their cause. Our client, a former member of The Masquerade, has asked us to take down the organization.\r\rHowever, it seems their first contract is a test of your skills. There are two parts to the test. If you complete it, our client will send us the rest of the contracts.\r\rGood Luck",
